# =============================================================================
# Environment Variables for zeeker-judgements
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to .env and fill in values as needed. Never commit .env.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Phase 1 (discovery) — no env vars required.
# The listing-page crawler uses only public HTML endpoints.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Phase 2 (content extraction) — no credentials required.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# HTML extraction uses the same httpx.Client as Phase 1 against public
# detail-page HTML at source_url. Operational knobs (batch cap, retry,
# quarantine TTL) are JUDGMENTS_EXTRACT_* env vars — see CLAUDE.md.
# Raw HTML and parsed extractions are cached under ./.cache/ (gitignored).

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Phase 3 (AI summaries, NOT YET IMPLEMENTED)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Any OpenAI-compatible LLM server: local (Ollama, vLLM) or cloud
# LLM_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1
# LLM_API_KEY=
# LLM_MODEL=llama3.1

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Deployment (NOT YET IMPLEMENTED — milestone defers S3 deploy)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# S3_BUCKET=
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=
# S3_ENDPOINT_URL=
